<subSubSection id="C30175E2FFA3FFB0C6F45648FDD5F87D" pageId="23" pageNumber="224" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="8BA42669FFA3FFB0C6F45648FCDDF835" blockId="23.[151,1437,1014,2013]" box="[199,848,1915,1941]" pageId="23" pageNumber="224">
<emphasis id="B96FFA7BFFA3FFB0C6F45648FEC3F835" bold="true" box="[199,334,1915,1941]" pageId="23" pageNumber="224">Etymology.</emphasis>
The species epithet refers to the 
<typeStatus id="54A098CBFFA3FFB0C48C5648FD62F835" box="[703,751,1915,1941]" pageId="23" pageNumber="224">type</typeStatus>
locality.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BA42669FFA3FFB0C6F456ADFDD5F87D" blockId="23.[151,1437,1014,2013]" pageId="23" pageNumber="224">
